- Good morning !
- Good morning !
- Why do you choose US ?
- i was considering during the last 6 months, between Finland, Germany and US. my final decision is US because it is the best country of education. moreover, it is more safe than Germany. and it is the best place to improve my English as well. So why not the US ?
- So, why do you choose MUM ?
- Yes, i was considering between MUM and Yale. But MUM had offered me a very attractive Financial Aid that i can not reject ! and Fairfield is a peaceful city. But honestly, if i had more money i would choose Yale.
- What do you do ?
- i am a software engineer, i develop websites and tools for my company.
- Who will pay for your study ?
- i do it myself.
- Great ! How much is your salary?
- It's about XX,000,000 VND (~X,X00 USD) do you want to see my Labor Contract ?
- No, thanks ! how much money have you saved ?
- *give her my bank statement* Yes, It is about 16,000 USD.
- How can you pay the tuition when your salary is X,X00 USD and your bank statement is just 16,000 USD ?
- As i said, MUM offered me a very good Financial Aid, I have to pay just only 3,000 USD for the first 8 months. do you want to see it ?
- Yes, Please
- Here, Please *give her the financial aid letter*. beside that, i will do practical training to earn money so that i can pay.
- How long is the program ?
- It's exactly 31 months.
- I see. How does the study help you on your career path ?
- There is a special team in my company, they research Machine Learning. I want to join that team, but i have to get more knowledge first ! (còn 1 lý do thứ 2 nói về dự định cá nhân ko tiện chia sẻ ở đây)
- So your salary will be increased then ?
- Yeah i think so, but...*frown a bit* (thái độ mình hơi nhăn nhó chút). There are many experts who are working on that team. my first priority are the experiences and knowledge of working with them. Money does not matter at all, I can make a lot of money after getting all the experiences i need !
- Will you apply the same company after graduate ?
- YES !!!
- That's great ! Congratulation, you are accepted ! enjoy your time in US !
- YESSSSS !!! Thanks a thousand times !!!. have a good day !!!


Hôm nay em cũng mới phỏng vấn ạ.
